org.lappsgrid.serialization.lif
[Groovy] Class Contains

java.lang.Object
  org.lappsgrid.serialization.lif.Contains

class Contains

Holds information for the 'contains' sections of a View's metadata section.

The contains metadata allows pipelines (planners or composers) to determine the contents of a ProcessingStep without having to traverse the contents of the annotations list.

Authors:
Keith Suderman
